# VEHICLE::GET_HELI_TAIL_BOOM_HEALTH

## Summary
Returns the health of the heli tail boom

## Parameters
* **VEHICLE_INDEX** vehicle

## Returns
* **FLOAT**

## Description
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Max 1000.
At -100 both helicopter rotors will stall.
